  "text": "We know it's hard to find the right gifts for your loved ones, so we've compiled a ton of fashion and beauty-focused gift guides tailored to a range of interests and budgets. Check out our latest below and find more right here.It's a simple truth that beauty people tend to have good taste. As natural seekers of newness and innovation, with a keen eye for aesthetics, they are among the best sources to consult when it comes to finding the most covetable gifts. So, we turned to some of the most trusted makeup artists, facialists, hairstylists, colorists and beauty founders out there to find out what they're buying this year.There are plenty of skin, hair, makeup and fragrance gift ideas, of course. An LED mask approved by an expert facialist who considers other models on the market \"trash\"? Yep. Candles co-signed by chic beauty founders? Yes, please. A reparative hair oil deemed a \"staple\" and \"perfect stocking stuffer\" by the pro colorist who took Kendall Jenner blonde? Sign me up.But the experts we consulted don't just have good taste when it comes to beauty products. They're also trendsetters and style trailblazers with their fingers on the pulse of what's cool right now. So they've highlighted a plush robe, joy-inducing handbags, luxuriously giftable socks, artful jewelry pieces, cozy knits and a surprisingly extensive selection of fashionable glassware as well.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesScroll through each of the galleries below for their picks.Sean Garrette, Esthetician \u0026 Beauty ExpertBabba C. Rivera, Founder \u0026 CEO of CeremoniaHeloise van Eeghen, Founder of Note PRCarol Han Pyle, Founder of NetteJaleesa Jaikaran, celebrity makeup artist and host of \"The Life of a Makeup Artist\" podcastJenna Perry, Celebrity Hair Colorist and Founder of Jenna Perry HairTina Chen Craig, Entrepreneur and U Beauty FounderJoseph Carrillo, Facial Sculptor and Makeup ArtistDianna Cohen, Founder of Crown AffairSofie Pavitt, Celebrity Facialist and Founder of Sofie Pavitt FaceDiarrha N'Diaye-Mbaye, Founder \u0026 CEO of Ami ColéElizabeth Grace Hand, esthetician and founder of Ställe StudiosRebecca Zhou, Founder \u0026 CEO of Soft Services Dr. Loretta Ciraldo, Dermatologist and Founder of Dr. LorettaCyndi Ramirez-Fulton, Founder \u0026 CEO of ChillhouseGeorgia Louise, Celebrity Facialist and Founder of Georgia Louise SkincareClayton Hawkins, Celebrity HairstylistTisha Thompson, Makeup Artist and Founder of LYS BeautySarah Akram, Celebrity FacialistDenise Vasi, Founder of MAED Beauty Kristyn Smith, Esthetician and Founder of Practise NYCAllison McNamara, Founder of MaraPlease note: Occasionally, we use affiliate links on our site. In no way does this affect our editorial decision-making.Tune into the Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.",
