  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWe know it\u0026#39;s hard to find the right gifts for your loved ones, so we\u0026#39;ve compiled a ton of fashion and beauty-focused gift guides tailored to a range of interests and budgets. Check out our latest below and \u003c/em\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/gift-guide\"\u003e\u003cem\u003efind more right here\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cem\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s a simple truth that beauty people tend to have good taste. As natural seekers of newness and innovation, with a keen eye for aesthetics, they are among the best sources to consult when it comes to finding the most covetable \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/gifts\"\u003egifts\u003c/a\u003e. So, we turned to some of the most trusted makeup artists, facialists, hairstylists, colorists and beauty founders out there to find out what they\u0026#39;re buying this year.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere are plenty of skin, hair, makeup and fragrance gift ideas, of course. An LED mask approved by an expert facialist who considers other models on the market \u0026#34;trash\u0026#34;? Yep. Candles co-signed by chic beauty founders? Yes, please. A reparative hair oil deemed a \u0026#34;staple\u0026#34; and \u0026#34;perfect stocking stuffer\u0026#34; by the pro colorist who took Kendall Jenner blonde? Sign me up.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut the experts we consulted don\u0026#39;t \u003cem\u003ejust\u003c/em\u003e have good taste when it comes to beauty products. They\u0026#39;re also trendsetters and style trailblazers with their fingers on the pulse of what\u0026#39;s cool right now. So they\u0026#39;ve highlighted a plush robe, joy-inducing handbags, luxuriously giftable socks, artful jewelry pieces, cozy knits and a surprisingly extensive selection of fashionable glassware as well.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eScroll through each of the galleries below for their picks.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"sean-garrette-esthetician-beauty-expert\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/seangarrette/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSean Garrette\u003c/a\u003e, Esthetician \u0026amp; Beauty Expert\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv phx-gallery=\"\"\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Agustina Bottoni Calici Milanesi Trio Glassware Set, $350, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://artemest.com/products/calici-milanesi-trio-glassware-set\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;: \u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;\u0026#34;I\u0026#39;m a bit of a snob when it comes to glassware. I\u0026#39;m that person that likes certain drinks and beverages in specific glassware! I\u0026#39;ve built quite the collection, and my current obsession are these ribbed cocktail glasses from Agustina Bottoni. Each piece is handmade in Italy by Master glassblowers using high-quality borosilicate glass.\u0026#34;\u0026amp;nbsp;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"833\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMTYzNjcx/agustina-bottoni-calici-milanesi-trio-glassware-set.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1276\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee361c700026bd\" data-image-slug=\"agustina-bottoni-calici-milanesi-trio-glassware-set\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMTYzNjcx\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Currentbody Skin LED Light Therapy Mask, $469, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+RUDzzvq4cFPqH8i6UGs4LQ\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;: \u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;\u0026#34;LED light therapy is one of my favorite modalities to use in the treatment room and at home. Red LED can help stimulate collagen, reduce fine lines, redness and inflammation in the skin. There are a lot of LED masks on the market that are trash, but Currentbody is legit. I\u0026#39;ve been using this brand for about three to four years and recommend it to my clients all the time.\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"679\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMTYzMzg5/currentbody-led-mask.jpg\" data-full-width=\"679\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee361c600026bd\" data-image-slug=\"currentbody-led-mask\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMTYzMzg5\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Guerlain Spiritueuse Double Vanille Eau De Parfum, $395, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://howl.link/uzxdfwuwbdv10\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;: \u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;\u0026#34;Guerlain makes some of the most incredible fragrances, and Double Vanille has become a staple in my collection. It\u0026#39;s the perfect fragrance for those that love gourmand, woody scents. It\u0026#39;s decadent, indulgent, rich and bold. It\u0026#39;s such a beautiful fragrance.\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"1278\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMjI5MjA3/guerlain-double-vanille-perfume.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1280\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee361c700126bd\" data-image-slug=\"guerlain-double-vanille-perfume\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMjI5MjA3\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_406%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjExMTY1NzI3NzYyMTYzNjcx/agustina-bottoni-calici-milanesi-trio-glassware-set.jpg\" alt=\"agustina-bottoni-calici-milanesi-trio-glassware-set\" itemprop=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"babba-c-rivera-founder-ceo-of-ceremonia\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/babba/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBabba C. Rivera\u003c/a\u003e, Founder \u0026amp; CEO of Ceremonia\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"heloise-van-eeghen-founder-of-note-pr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/superhelder\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHeloise van Eeghen\u003c/a\u003e, Founder of Note PR\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"carol-han-pyle-founder-of-nette\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/carolhan\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eCarol Han Pyle\u003c/a\u003e, Founder of Nette\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"jaleesa-jaikaran-celebrity-makeup-artist-and-host-of-the-life-of-a-makeup-artist-podcast\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jaleesajaikaran\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eJaleesa Jaikaran\u003c/a\u003e, celebrity makeup artist and host of \u0026#34;The Life of a Makeup Artist\u0026#34; podcast\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"jenna-perry-celebrity-hair-colorist-and-founder-of-jenna-perry-hair\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jennaperryhair\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eJenna Perry\u003c/a\u003e, Celebrity Hair Colorist and Founder of Jenna Perry Hair\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"tina-chen-craig-entrepreneur-and-u-beauty-founder\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tinachencraig/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTina Chen Craig\u003c/a\u003e, Entrepreneur and U Beauty Founder\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv phx-gallery=\"\"\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Self-Portrait Silver Crystal Heart Clutch, $585, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+dFPASNP7hJR7dzC6oWwsnA\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;:\u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;\u0026amp;nbsp;\u0026#34;A little self-love never hurt anyone. Topped with their signature bow, Self-Portrait\u0026#39;s decadent heart-shaped clutch is a great reminder that she is loved.\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"1704\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzI1MzM1/self-portrait-crystal-heart-clutch.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1835\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee3663f00027d7\" data-image-slug=\"self-portrait-crystal-heart-clutch\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzI1MzM1\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;U Beauty Resurfacing Flash Peel, $188, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+xfbhYCinvliVQLsLkv8tkQ\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;:\u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt; \u0026#34;Who doesn\u0026#39;t want fresh, smooth, new-looking skin in just five minutes? Visibly resurfacing, restoring and renewing your skin simultaneously in record time, the Resurfacing Flash Peel is a first-of-its-kind, clinical-grade chemical exfoliator that gives more than it takes. It\u0026#39;s perfect for the skin-care enthusiast who\u0026#39;s too busy for 90-minute facial treatments and in-office peels — the girl who\u0026#39;s got no time for downtime!\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"1051\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzkwODcx/u-beauty-flash-peel.jpg\" data-full-width=\"663\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee3663e00127d7\" data-image-slug=\"u-beauty-flash-peel\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzkwODcx\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Nicky Hilton For Rebecca Valence Alivia Short Sleeve Mini Dress, $840, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+QHt9E1IAtgaKP6iXUtBCCQ\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;: \u0026#34;Nicky Hilton x Rebecca Valence dresses are my current go-to for party season. Flirty, not fussy, the Alivia is a festive-chic mini that will take you beyond the holidays.\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"2000\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzI1MDUz/nicky-hilton-rebecca-vallance-alivia-short-sleeve-mini-dress.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1333\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee3664000027d7\" data-image-slug=\"nicky-hilton-rebecca-vallance-alivia-short-sleeve-mini-dress\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzI1MDUz\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Apollo Wearable Vagus Nerve Stimulator \u0026amp;amp; Reset Vibrating Wristband, $350 $300, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+ame4Y_n99jZDY4vZxrL-zA\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;:\u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt; \u0026#34;I discovered Apollo over the summer and since then, rarely travel without it. During long flights, I wear it to keep me calm, and it really does help with nerves. If I wake up in the middle of the night and can\u0026#39;t go back to sleep, I grab my Apollo and set it sleep mode — it\u0026#39;s so comforting. And if I find myself starting to doze off during a midday meeting, setting it to energy mode is like a shot of espresso.\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"549\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzkwNTg5/apollo-wearable.jpg\" data-full-width=\"679\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee3663e00227d7\" data-image-slug=\"apollo-wearable\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzkwNTg5\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_406%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjExMTY2MDM0ODUyMzI1MzM1/self-portrait-crystal-heart-clutch.jpg\" alt=\"self-portrait-crystal-heart-clutch\" itemprop=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"joseph-carrillo-facial-sculptor-and-makeup-artist\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/josephcarrillo/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eJoseph Carrillo\u003c/a\u003e, Facial Sculptor and Makeup Artist\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"dianna-cohen-founder-of-crown-affair\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/diannacohen\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eDianna Cohen\u003c/a\u003e, Founder of Crown Affair\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"sofie-pavitt-celebrity-facialist-and-founder-of-sofie-pavitt-face\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sofiepavitt\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSofie Pavitt\u003c/a\u003e, Celebrity Facialist and Founder of Sofie Pavitt Face\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"diarrha-n-diaye-mbaye-founder-ceo-of-ami-col\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/diarrhaxo/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eDiarrha N\u0026#39;Diaye-Mbaye\u003c/a\u003e, Founder \u0026amp; CEO of Ami Colé\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"elizabeth-grace-hand-esthetician-and-founder-of-st-lle-studios\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/elizabethgracehand/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eElizabeth Grace Hand\u003c/a\u003e, esthetician and founder of Ställe Studios\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"rebecca-zhou-founder-ceo-of-soft-services\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rebecca.zhou/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRebecca Zhou\u003c/a\u003e, Founder \u0026amp; CEO of Soft Services \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv phx-gallery=\"\"\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Alessi Blip Spoon Rest, $35, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+4Ztn3sT7DdXn0aJHImgT6Q\u0026#34;\u0026gt;available here\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;:\u0026lt;/strong\u0026gt;\u0026amp;nbsp;\u0026#34;My husband stocks this Alessi Spoon Rest at his art/design store upstate, Corners. I buy these often as gifts, but rebrand them as jewelry dishes. At only $35, it\u0026#39;s a chic, novel and wallet-friendly option. It\u0026#39;s what I\u0026#39;m bringing if I find myself needing something for a White Elephant this year.\u0026#34;\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"989\" data-full-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjExMTY2MjYxNjgwMjg1NjU1/alessi-blip-spoon-rest.jpg\" data-full-width=\"1159\" data-image-id=\"ci02ee3698b00027d7\" data-image-slug=\"alessi-blip-spoon-rest\" data-public-id=\"MjExMTY2MjYxNjgwMjg1NjU1\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;\u0026lt;strong\u0026gt;Coming Soon The Pill, $145, \u0026lt;a href=\u0026#34;https://rstyle.me/+Egn5o0EcbDNVwYAGu5